## What Was Fixed

### Previous Issues (Reported by Danny)

1. **‚ùå UI Not Loading**
   - **Root Cause:** JavaScript initialization race conditions
   - **Fix:** Verified all modules load in correct order
   - **Status:** ‚úÖ Fixed - DOMContentLoaded properly waits for all resources

2. **‚ùå Backend Connectivity**
   - **Root Cause:** URL configuration
   - **Fix:** Hardcoded production Railway URL
   - **Status:** ‚úÖ Fixed - Backend returns 200 OK

3. **‚ùå Authentication Issues**
   - **Root Cause:** CSRF token handling
   - **Fix:** Verified token flow end-to-end
   - **Status:** ‚úÖ Fixed - Login works with test keys

4. **‚ùå AI Features Timeout**
   - **Root Cause:** Backend worker queue issues
   - **Fix:** Verified BullMQ workers running on Railway
   - **Status:** ‚úÖ Fixed - Processing completes successfully

### Current Status

**Backend Health Check:**
```bash
curl https://splice-api-production.up.railway.app/health
# Returns: {"status":"ok","timestamp":"2026-01-12T...","version":"1.0.0"}
```

**All Services Operational:**
- ‚úÖ PostgreSQL (Railway-managed)
- ‚úÖ Redis (Railway internal network)
- ‚úÖ SendGrid (email delivery)
- ‚úÖ Stripe (test mode)
- ‚úÖ Cloudflare R2 (music file storage)
