macOS Version: [e.g., Sonoma 14.2]
SPLICE Version: 6.0.8
```

### 2. Verification Script Output
```bash
cd /Users/imorgado/SPLICE
./verify-installation.sh > verification_output.txt
```

### 3. Diagnostic Logs
1. Open SPLICE panel
2. Click Debug button (üîç)
3. Click "Run Diagnostics"
4. Copy all output

### 4. Browser Console
1. Open http://localhost:8092/
2. Click "SPLICE" panel
3. Copy all `[SPLICE]` log entries
4. Include any red errors

### 5. Screenshots
- Panel UI showing the issue
- Any error dialogs or messages
- Chrome debugger if relevant

